    height: 16px;"></span></small>
                                                        </a></p>
                                                                                                        <p>Allamah Baqir al-Majlisi: <span> ضعيف على المشهور  </span> - Mir‘at al ‘Uqul Fi Sharh Akhbar Al al Rasul (8/27)</p>
                                                                                                                                        
